WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.225
=Episode 12=

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:53.640
Dad,

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:55.399
I almost caught Ye Chen,

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:56.679
but Aoxue suddenly meddled!

00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:58.460
She insisted on an one-on-one fight
with him.

00:00:58.479 --> 00:00:59.560
Then Ye Chen suddenly...

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:00.719
Enough!

00:01:01.640 --> 00:01:03.799
Aoxue went to clean up your mess.

00:01:04.359 --> 00:01:05.600
And you're blaming her for it?

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.900
I think you've become more useless
by the day.

00:01:08.359 --> 00:01:09.875
Dad, don't worry. How about this?

00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.599
I'll bring over some men
and take the vase back...

00:01:11.599 --> 00:01:12.359
It's too late!

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:16.181
What we should be thinking about now is

00:01:16.462 --> 00:01:19.037
whether Ye Chen
will come steal our things.

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:25.000
What's wrong, Aoxue?

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.480
Why are you crying?

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:27.660
What happened, sweetheart?

00:01:28.519 --> 00:01:30.439
(A woman acted strangely on the street)
It's because of the video.

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:31.520
(Performance art or a sudden incident?)

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.040
Go.

00:01:34.380 --> 00:01:36.040
Tell that blogger
to take the video down.

00:01:36.050 --> 00:01:38.120
Tell him I'm sending a lawyer's letter
to sue him.

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.319
I-I'll handle it.

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:40.290
I'll take care of it now.

00:01:41.319 --> 00:01:42.400
What a mess.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.519
This is so embarrassing.

00:01:44.519 --> 00:01:46.799
- This is beyond embarrassing!
- Alright, c'mon.

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:48.159
Don't cry anymore. Be good.

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.200
Listen to me.

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.040
Some bloggers these days

00:01:51.239 --> 00:01:52.079
will say anything

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:53.680
just for a bit of traffic.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.480
You know why?

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:55.900
Because no one keeps them in check.

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.840
What I want to remind you of is

00:01:59.079 --> 00:02:00.480
that Ye Chen

00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:01.480
is quite cunning too.

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:03.079
Just like those bloggers,

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:05.959
he used some underhanded tricks
to beat you.

00:02:06.319 --> 00:02:07.480
So you shouldn't feel ashamed.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.040
My little sweetheart,

00:02:09.719 --> 00:02:10.760
you are absolutely

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.079
the best.

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:17.439
This is so humiliating!

00:02:17.439 --> 00:02:19.375
Everyone saw it!

00:02:19.375 --> 00:02:20.879
Alright, stop crying.

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:50.759
You're back.

00:02:54.190 --> 00:02:55.599
Did you fall asleep waiting for me?

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:57.400
Are you alright?

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:59.280
Look what I brought you.

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:04.250
Returned to its rightful owner.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.800
It really is Grandpa's medicine jar.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:08.439
Yeah.

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:11.960
Thank you, Ye Chen.

00:03:12.919 --> 00:03:14.199
No, I should be thanking you.

00:03:14.639 --> 00:03:16.360
If I hadn't gone to the Ghost Market

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:17.199
to look for this jar,

00:03:17.390 --> 00:03:18.439
I wouldn't have remembered

00:03:18.439 --> 00:03:20.600
that Mr. Quan once taught me
how to appraise antiques.

00:03:21.090 --> 00:03:23.080
Did you change the chip
in your brain recently?

00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:25.199
Why are there so many surprises lately?

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:28.280
I think it's more like

00:03:28.825 --> 00:03:30.345
a system reboot.

00:03:31.275 --> 00:03:32.754
I'll make sure you realize

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:33.840
you've found yourself

00:03:34.175 --> 00:03:35.934
a treasure of a boyfriend.

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:38.599
More like a smug boyfriend.

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:41.000
By the way,

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:44.199
why is the Qin family
so determined to take that vase?

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:49.120
I think

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.000
it's probably because

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.950
the two of us teamed up
to confront them earlier.

00:03:53.010 --> 00:03:55.640
They're still holding a grudge,
so they purposely create trouble.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:03:59.100
Let's not talk about that.

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.879
You're the chairman now.

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.639
You should focus
on cooperating well with Dihao Group.

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:06.439
You've got big responsibilities.

00:04:06.675 --> 00:04:08.146
Just focus on your work.

00:04:13.475 --> 00:04:15.087
(Welcome Home, Residents)

00:04:15.700 --> 00:04:17.680
You should've stayed home
and gotten some rest.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.800
Why did you come out?

00:04:19.737 --> 00:04:21.474
We need to have a proper celebration.

00:04:22.020 --> 00:04:23.458
And scout a venue while we're at it.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.319
Does it really have to be this grand?

00:04:25.319 --> 00:04:26.680
Of course it does.

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:29.160
And I've got another surprise for you.

00:04:31.412 --> 00:04:32.000
(Challenge Letter)

00:04:35.340 --> 00:04:36.500
(You caught me off guard last time,
so it doesn't count.)

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:37.400
(Let's have a rematch in three days!)

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:43.639
Aoxue, right?

00:04:44.040 --> 00:04:45.199
Let me give you some advice.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:47.370
Better to settle grudges
than deepen them.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:48.520
Let's just let this go.

00:04:48.660 --> 00:04:49.040
Come on.

00:04:49.162 --> 00:04:49.839
No way!

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:51.400
Meet me at the gym in three days.

00:04:51.410 --> 00:04:52.500
We'll have a proper fight.

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:53.800
I'll make sure everyone knows

00:04:54.079 --> 00:04:55.319
that Qin Aoxue is no weakling.

00:04:56.959 --> 00:04:58.800
Of course you're not a weakling.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.600
Then who is she?

00:05:00.319 --> 00:05:01.399
Let me introduce her.

00:05:01.879 --> 00:05:04.240
She's the fiercest little chili
in the universe.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:05.240
You happy?

00:05:05.439 --> 00:05:06.600
Fame means nothing.

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:09.319
Just let the wind carry it away.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:11.000
Ye Chen, why are you such a coward?

00:05:11.190 --> 00:05:12.759
And you call yourself a martial artist?

00:05:13.162 --> 00:05:13.959
Don't you know

00:05:13.959 --> 00:05:16.490
I'm the most useless live-in son-in-law
in the entire universe?

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:17.639
Alright, stop talking.

00:05:17.650 --> 00:05:18.240
We're leaving.

00:05:19.079 --> 00:05:19.500
Oh right!

00:05:20.079 --> 00:05:20.920
Tell your father

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.790
I've already retired
from the martial world.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.040
Tell him not to bother me,

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.100
even if something comes up.

00:05:26.839 --> 00:05:27.879
What a lunatic.

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:42.519
Listen, let me explain.

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:45.920
My engagement to Wang Yunfei was forced
by our families.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.439
I don't like him at all.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.439
Nothing ever happened between us.

00:05:50.199 --> 00:05:51.560
Can you just give me some peace?

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:53.920
Aodong,

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:55.240
only after meeting you

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:56.975
did I finally understand
what a real man is

00:05:56.975 --> 00:05:58.040
and what true love is.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:58.560
Wait.

00:05:59.210 --> 00:06:00.950
Is this a place
someone like you can come?

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:03.319
What,

00:06:03.519 --> 00:06:04.639
did you own this place?

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:08.000
Or are only rich young masters like you
and spoiled heiresses like her

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.000
allowed to come here?

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:10.800
This is Buckingham Palace.

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:12.639
Only VIPs can enter, understand?

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:14.439
And how do you know I'm not a VIP?

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.439
VIP membership requires
a ten-million deposit.

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.759
Do you have that?

00:06:18.759 --> 00:06:19.812
Ten million?

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:20.519
Yup.

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:21.519
Hey you!

00:06:21.750 --> 00:06:23.079
What kind of management is this?

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:25.480
Why did you let trash like him in?

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:26.900
Are we supposed to dine

00:06:26.900 --> 00:06:27.861
with people like this?

00:06:28.075 --> 00:06:29.600
Why haven't you thrown him out yet?

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:30.990
Just looking at him ruins my appetite.

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:32.319
Sir, ma'am,

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:33.319
I'm very sorry.

00:06:33.959 --> 00:06:36.240
Mr. Ye has just officially become

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:39.575
a Platinum Distinguished Member,
even higher than VIP.

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:45.439
I came here to check out the place.

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:47.439
But since the two of you are here,

00:06:47.800 --> 00:06:48.560
this meal is on me.

00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:55.340
(Li, call the guys over
to Buckingham Palace.)

00:06:55.340 --> 00:06:57.175
(I need a favor.
Bring as many people as possible.)

00:06:57.319 --> 00:06:58.160
Please wait a moment.

00:06:58.200 --> 00:06:59.520
My friends will be here shortly.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.360
Enjoy your meal.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:12.600
Chen,

00:07:12.879 --> 00:07:14.240
this isn't us helping you.

00:07:14.519 --> 00:07:16.399
You're the one treating us
to a big feast!

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:17.560
Thank you, Chen!

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:20.079
The fact that you all came today

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:21.519
is already the biggest help to me.

00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:23.279
Everyone, eat as much as you like.

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:24.360
- Alright!
- Alright!

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:24.959
Sure.

00:07:24.959 --> 00:07:25.800
Come on, everyone.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.720
- Thank you, Chen!
- Thank you, Chen!

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:30.240
Go ahead and eat.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:38.360
Go on, eat!

00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:39.300
What are you waiting for?

00:07:39.319 --> 00:07:40.220
I'm paying, it's fine.

00:07:48.550 --> 00:07:50.680
You people are acting so superior
over a simple meal.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.600
Look at you showing off.

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:55.800
Bro.

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:56.390
Yes, Mr. Ye?

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:57.959
I'd like to reserve

00:07:57.959 --> 00:08:00.879
the Sky Garden upstairs
to have dinner with my wife.

00:08:01.160 --> 00:08:02.360
Mr. Ye, I'm sorry.

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:04.120
Since Buckingham Palace opened,

00:08:04.439 --> 00:08:06.040
we've never offered private bookings.

00:08:10.512 --> 00:08:11.837
There's always a first time.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.199
Just do me this favor.

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:14.279
Please.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:16.680
Mr. Ye, you're really good to your wife.

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:17.959
For that alone,

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:19.237
I'll arrange it right away.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:20.399
Thank you, thank you.

00:08:23.887 --> 00:08:27.220
♪You're always drifting near,
then far away♪

00:08:27.487 --> 00:08:30.562
♪Like a wandering cloud in the sky♪

00:08:30.637 --> 00:08:33.350
♪You always leave me hard to read♪

00:08:33.925 --> 00:08:37.062
♪So I can only follow like your shadow♪

00:08:38.580 --> 00:08:41.900
♪My eyes flicker between light and dark♪

00:08:42.100 --> 00:08:45.337
♪Only because of you
they change like the weather♪

00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:47.900
♪Tears drift low through the air
for no reason♪

00:08:48.039 --> 00:08:49.000
Buckingham Palace.

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:51.320
Grandpa designed it himself back then.

00:08:51.725 --> 00:08:53.425
♪But they're just echoes of longing♪

00:08:53.562 --> 00:08:55.325
♪Ticking on until the dawn♪

00:08:55.330 --> 00:08:56.679
Why are there so many people here?

00:08:58.480 --> 00:08:59.980
(No other guest is allowed.)
This must be the first time

00:08:59.980 --> 00:09:01.260
Buckingham Palace
has been fully reserved, right?

00:09:01.559 --> 00:09:03.639
I heard a mysterious tycoon booked it

00:09:03.639 --> 00:09:05.600
to spend a romantic evening
with his wife.

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:08.480
His wife must be so lucky.

00:09:09.399 --> 00:09:11.450
Mr. Ye and Ms. Xiao,

00:09:11.679 --> 00:09:13.960
we warmly welcome you
to Buckingham Palace.

00:09:14.759 --> 00:09:15.960
- Welcome.
- Welcome.

00:09:29.679 --> 00:09:30.600
Ye Chen,

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.240
are you the mysterious tycoon

00:09:33.879 --> 00:09:35.200
everyone outside is talking about?

00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:36.559
Don't I look the part?

00:09:37.159 --> 00:09:38.240
Aren't I mysterious enough?

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:39.480
Rich enough?

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:41.879
What's going on?

00:09:42.710 --> 00:09:43.799
You'll know once we go in.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.039
- Welcome.
- Welcome.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.200
Now that's the real mysterious tycoon.

00:10:01.159 --> 00:10:02.600
Aren't they just acting?

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:04.600
But they don't know
that you already know.

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:06.720
So I let them keep acting.

00:10:07.300 --> 00:10:09.880
Otherwise, who could afford
to book the entire Buckingham Palace?

00:10:09.900 --> 00:10:11.500
How can you play both sides like this?

00:10:11.639 --> 00:10:13.720
Actually, has never...

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:17.990
Just pretend you didn't see through it.

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:19.799
Let's do a good deed.

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:21.600
Watch your expressions.

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:27.039
Hi.

00:10:30.137 --> 00:10:32.502
Book the Sky Garden
at Buckingham Palace?

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.960
Mr. Ye, isn't this a bit too...

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:35.480
Flashy?

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:38.840
Xiao Churan will definitely...

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:39.600
Get suspicious.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:41.840
That's why

00:10:42.279 --> 00:10:44.200
I need the two of you
to keep acting for me.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:46.320
Does it have to be Buckingham Palace?

00:10:46.437 --> 00:10:48.240
Yes it has to be Buckingham Palace.

00:10:48.575 --> 00:10:50.840
Because that place
means something special to Churan.

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:52.120
Only then

00:10:52.639 --> 00:10:53.919
can she truly feel

00:10:53.919 --> 00:10:56.120
the overwhelming love I have for her.

00:10:56.559 --> 00:10:57.360
Love...

00:10:59.840 --> 00:11:02.840
Love...

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.480
Love!

00:11:09.050 --> 00:11:09.919
This isn't just love!

00:11:09.919 --> 00:11:11.399
It's romance!

00:11:11.879 --> 00:11:12.879
That's so touching.

00:11:13.399 --> 00:11:14.360
I think

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:15.799
we have to help him with this.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.960
Don't you agree,

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:17.399
Ms. Wang?

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:18.600
Mm.

00:11:19.399 --> 00:11:20.480
Sorry, Churan.

00:11:20.490 --> 00:11:21.990
I have to trouble you two again today.

00:11:22.280 --> 00:11:23.600
No, we're the ones troubling you.

00:11:26.039 --> 00:11:27.300
There's an issue at the company.

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:28.350
I have to head back first.

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.240
Sorry.

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.279
That urgent?

00:11:30.279 --> 00:11:30.639
Yes.

00:11:30.639 --> 00:11:31.840
Company matters can't wait.

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:35.159
Daokun, don't you have
something urgent too?

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:36.679
Uh... no, I'm fine.

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.480
The food hasn't even been served yet.

00:11:39.639 --> 00:11:41.360
Don't you need to give me a ride?

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.679
Of course...

00:11:45.679 --> 00:11:46.639
I'll give you a ride.

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:48.559
Then sorry, we'll head out first.

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:50.080
The bill's already been paid.

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:51.190
Don't let the food go to waste.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:52.175
But...

00:11:52.180 --> 00:11:53.460
- Don't waste it!
- You're leaving?

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:55.720
Kun, the dishes
haven't even been served yet.

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:57.159
Dongxue!

00:11:58.279 --> 00:11:58.799
But...

00:11:58.799 --> 00:11:59.600
They're already gone.

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:27.200
When Grandpa designed
this Buckingham Palace,

00:12:27.919 --> 00:12:29.240
I was still in elementary school.

00:12:30.137 --> 00:12:32.537
It was the work he was most proud of
in his entire life.

00:12:33.759 --> 00:12:34.320
Churan,

00:12:34.919 --> 00:12:37.960
I believe you'll design something
just as amazing as Grandpa did.

00:12:38.919 --> 00:12:39.639
Cheers.

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:47.240
Ye Chen.

00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:49.000
Thank you.

00:12:49.700 --> 00:12:50.590
How will you thank me?

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.790
How do you want me to thank you?

00:12:53.879 --> 00:12:55.919
Our marriage agreement
is almost up, right?

00:12:57.960 --> 00:13:00.879
So tell me, when can I officially
become your husband?

00:13:02.159 --> 00:13:03.960
So this is what you've been waiting for.

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:07.039
I'm just trying to try my luck.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.159
In that case...

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:11.960
I'll think about it.

00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:15.679
Then I'll wait for your good news.

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:16.960
Mmm.

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:20.679
Madam Li.

00:13:20.679 --> 00:13:21.960
When were you discharged
from the hospital?

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:23.080
Why didn't you tell me?

00:13:23.080 --> 00:13:24.159
I could've gone to pick you up.

00:13:24.159 --> 00:13:26.062
Chen wouldn't let me say anything.

00:13:26.100 --> 00:13:27.799
He said he wanted
to give you a surprise.

00:13:31.679 --> 00:13:32.639
Osmanthus cakes?

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:34.960
Thank you, Madam Li.

00:13:35.919 --> 00:13:36.320
Churan,

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:38.000
I got very ill once when I was a kid.

00:13:38.799 --> 00:13:40.399
I couldn't eat anything

00:13:40.399 --> 00:13:41.919
and I survived on her osmanthus cakes.

00:13:43.799 --> 00:13:45.159
Delicious!

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:46.279
I want some too!

00:13:47.350 --> 00:13:52.362
♪If dreams are truly out of reach♪

00:13:52.625 --> 00:13:56.887
♪Then how did I end up meeting you?♪

00:13:58.100 --> 00:14:02.580
♪If everything is destined♪

00:14:02.580 --> 00:14:07.340
♪Then how can I get closer to you?♪

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:12.399
Madam Li,

00:14:12.759 --> 00:14:13.960
let us take you home.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:14.960
No need.

00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:16.159
The doctor

00:14:16.159 --> 00:14:18.120
recommended I get a bit more exercise.

00:14:18.700 --> 00:14:21.480
Madam Li, make sure you take good care
of your health once you're home.

00:14:21.900 --> 00:14:23.960
When Ye Chen and I have time,
we'll come visit you.

00:14:24.240 --> 00:14:24.639
Alright.

00:14:24.840 --> 00:14:25.360
Don't worry.

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:26.990
You two head back now.

00:14:27.300 --> 00:14:28.440
Inform us when you get home.

00:14:28.919 --> 00:14:29.440
Be careful.

00:14:33.399 --> 00:14:34.159
- Let's go.
- Mmm.

00:15:25.612 --> 00:15:28.100
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:15:28.187 --> 00:15:31.940
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:15:32.400 --> 00:15:37.337
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:39.787
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:15:40.100 --> 00:15:42.780
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:15:43.850 --> 00:15:46.475
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:15:46.775 --> 00:15:49.787
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:15:49.987 --> 00:15:53.037
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:15:53.150 --> 00:15:56.112
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:15:56.380 --> 00:15:59.537
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:15:59.762 --> 00:16:03.512
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:16:03.512 --> 00:16:06.375
♪I belong to no one♪

00:16:06.437 --> 00:16:09.887
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:16:09.887 --> 00:16:12.562
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:16:12.562 --> 00:16:18.900
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪